PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Larry Lee HOUSTON, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157374
157375
COA: 341909
341911 Supreme Court of Michigan. December 21, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the February 28, 2018 orders of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
